Note: Runa AI Framework - Meta-Strategy Systems
Production-grade meta-strategy orchestration with intelligent strategy-of-strategies management, hierarchical coordination, and strategic architecture governance
Competitive with enterprise strategic portfolio platforms, strategic architecture systems, and advanced strategy orchestration engines :End Note

Note: Core meta-strategy types for comprehensive strategic governance
Type MetaStrategyType as Union containing:
    "portfolio_meta_strategy",
    "hierarchical_meta_strategy",
    "ecosystem_meta_strategy",
    "adaptive_meta_strategy",
    "learning_meta_strategy",
    "orchestration_meta_strategy",
    "governance_meta_strategy",
    "evolutionary_meta_strategy",
    "coordination_meta_strategy",
    "architecture_meta_strategy"

Note: Comprehensive meta-strategy definition with intelligent governance
Type called "MetaStrategyDefinition":
    "meta_strategy_id" as String,
    "meta_strategy_name" as String,
    "meta_strategy_type" as MetaStrategyType,
    "governed_strategies" as List[Dictionary],
    "coordination_rules" as Dictionary,
    "governance_policies" as Dictionary,
    "orchestration_parameters" as Dictionary,
    "meta_objectives" as List[Dictionary],
    "strategic_architecture" as Dictionary,
    "meta_strategy_metadata" as Dictionary

