Note: Utility processes for ID generation
Process called "generate_strategic_architecture_id" that takes nothing returns String:
    Let timestamp be current_timestamp[]
    Let random_component be generate_secure_random[16]
    Let architecture_hash be calculate_hash[timestamp Joined with random_component]
    Return "strategy_arch_" Joined with architecture_hash

Process called "generate_ecosystem_evolution_id" that takes nothing returns String:
    Let timestamp be current_timestamp[]
    Let random_component be generate_secure_random[14]
    Let evolution_hash be calculate_hash[timestamp Joined with random_component]
    Return "ecosystem_evo_" Joined with evolution_hash